{"tid":2241762,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐盟：明日起對中國進口的鋁型材徵收30.4%至48%的關稅","createTime":"2020-10-13T14:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:26:38.000Z","uid":28114,"like":523,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec3b03bafa4cd2bb1e6ab93e6c27447ecb5775f","tid":2241762,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"《路透社》報道，歐盟官方公報於今日表示，在對中國生產商是否以不公平的低價出售貨品的調查期間，將會在明日起對中國進口的鋁型材徵收30.4%至48%的關稅。歐盟表示，這些關稅只是臨時性，但是若4月份完成的調查發現中國生產商違規，屆時將會向它們徵收為期5年的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n負責協調27個成員國的貿易政策的歐盟委員會2月開始收到歐洲鋁工業的投訴，指中國進口的鋁產品違反貿易規定。歐洲鋁工業成員包括挪威的海德魯公司（Norsk Hydro）、英國的力拓集團（Rio Tinto）、美國的鋁業公司（Alcoa）等。不過，同時間，中國金屬協會稱歐盟及歐洲鋁工業的申訴毫無根據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/660662274644975/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F127745917936616%2Fposts%2F660662274644975%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=d6516887\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/660662274644975/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"843f741dbc123693054f6bc8d9e7d28de882c24a","tid":2241762,"uid":28114,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"貿易戰新軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393774dc9b46258f98d71672377627599c965f76","tid":2241762,"uid":104138,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"果時EU 就話美國野蠻，見美國收到咁開心，中國又肯比又想玩埋一份"},{"pid":"fe4dbe8ea69a0e7b4140a72dc66c1f1ce099c4b7","tid":2241762,"uid":155095,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"歐盟其實同時向美國開刀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2774773/0_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2774773%2F0_1024.png&h=e0d3675b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p